      "decision": "Omit",
      "description": "Show Posted button only when processed and accounting view is enabled",
      "impactIfOmitted": "Posted button is always hidden in the simplified UI",
      "reason": "Posted button is part of the classic-only accounting UX, not exposed in the MVP"
    },
